name: Alpacawhal
description: For almost one year, I engaged in a performance artwork called "Alpcawhal", a communications exploration disguised as an art magazine. The magazine eventually reached hundreds of daily website visitors and had almost 1500 Twitter followers. This PDF contains 44 articles across 473 pages from the alpacawhal.com website and will be the only associated artwork released to the public related to the project as a commemoration. 3bbbb9f6eae2025c
